name: __EDataRegistryAcquireStatus
doc: State of a registry async request

InitialAcquireFinished: Temporary state, finished acquiring data but need to check resources
WaitingForResources: Data requested and returned, still loading dependent resources
AcquireError: Failed to acquire, may have timed out or had network issues, can be retried later
DoesNotExist: Known to not exist, cannot be retried
